NAME

    XML::Twig - Tree interface to XML documents allowing processing chunk
                by chunk of huge documents.
                

SUMMARY (see Twig.pod for full details)

    single-tree mode    
        my $t= new XML::Twig();
        $t->parsefile( 'doc.xml');
        $t->print;

    chunk mode 
        my $t= new XML::Twig( Handlers => { section => \&flush});
        $t->parsefile( 'doc.xml');
        $t->flush;
        sub flush { $_[0]->flush; }
    
INSTALLATION

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

CHANGES

    This is version 1.7.
    DTD interface added. 
    StartHandlers Added.
    Various bugs fixed

    Note: the DTD interface is in ALPHA mode (ie it may be changed in 
    the future)

